&lt;p&gt;FIXED TERM / SECONDMENT until 31.03.21&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a band 8b Senior Clinical Manager.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will define current processes, facilitate discussions and advise colleagues as to how best practice might be adopted in the definition of future processes, document those processes as they are agreed and oversee their delivery. &lt;br /&gt;The post forms a key part of the North East &amp; Yorkshire Nursing clinical leadership team. The post-holder will provide credible, effective and visible professional nursing leadership at the local area and will make a corporate contribution in achieving implementation of the NHS England strategy and the Vision for Nurses, Midwives and Care Givers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;BASE: NHSE staff are currently working from home. If this is to change the base will be within the North East &amp; Yorkshire Region.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a short term contract to cover a secondment of a member of staff.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Wendy Barker&lt;/p&gt;
